      "value": "<p>Your clan have always been more at home in the open ocean. You can breath underwater, You have a 30ft swimming speed, 60ft at 7th level, and 90ft at 18th level. If you take a short rest near a body of water that you can submerge at least half of your body in, you may recover additional Chakra and HP equal to twice your level.</p>",
